</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Massive parallelization of serial inference algorithms for a complex generalized linear model</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Suchard%20MA"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Marc A Suchard</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
