<sup>5</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Madigan%20D"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id5"><span class="name western">David Madigan</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id5">
<h3><span class="name western">David Madigan</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>4</sup>Department of Statistics, Columbia University, New York, NY, USA
</div>
