<cite>d’Esopo D. A convex programming procedure. Naval Research Logistics Quarterly. 1959;6:33–42.</cite> [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Naval%20Research%20Logistics%20Quarterly&amp;title=A%20convex%20programming%20procedure&amp;author=D%20d%E2%80%99Esopo&amp;volume=6&amp;publication_year=1959&amp;pages=33-42&amp;" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Scholar</a>]</li>
